<h1><span id="Hungarian_Defence">Hungarian Defence</span></h1>
<p>This defence is seldom seen, but has a reputation of being solid. Its aim is to defend against an eventual queen exchange and against a pawn storm on the king side.
</p><p>White's best choice is to attack the center with 4. d4. 4. O-O is also an option, despite being a bit passive.
</p>
